 and silverbeet, push down with aid of spatula and cook <b>2 min\/100°C\/\/speed 2<b> (see Tips)."},{"content":"Add lemon juice, parsley and pepper and mix <b>5 sec\/\/speed 2<b>. Add additional lemon juice and salt to taste, then divide between bowls to serve."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> or <i>Everyday Cookbook<\/i> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe.","We serve this as a chunky soup, but you can blend it to make it smooth. After cooking the kale and silverbeet, blend <strong>1 min\/speed 4-10, increasing speed gradually from speed 4 to speed 10.<\/strong> Proceed as per recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","30m","4 portions"]}